Among the big names on the move, fellow AI cloud company  CoreWeave  popped 18%, AI chip maker  Advanced Micro Devices  was up 3.3%, and networking-equipment company  Arista Networks  was rising 5.9%.  Palantir Technologies  also got in on the action.
